# i18n and Copy Rules

- Keep user-facing text in i18n dictionaries (`en.ts` and `bn.ts`).
- For dynamic strings, follow existing function-key pattern where applicable.
- Add/update keys in both locales in the same change.
- Do not leave placeholder or untranslated strings in production routes/components.
- Form field obligation markers use `common.optional` and `common.requiredForReview`; hints describe purpose only (see `55-field-requirements.mdc` and `docs/form-field-conventions.md`).
